snippet.title: Bomb Club Deluxe - Trailer (En)
snippet.description:
If you have a knack for explosives, the Bomb Club welcomes you! Meet new bombs, uncover new challenges, and create awesome chain reactions in this explosive puzzle game!

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1771440/Bomb_Club_Deluxe/
Website: http://bombclubdeluxe.sos-webcomic.com/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/AntoineLatour
